		"description": "Complete API collection for the AI Schedule Manager with authentication, CRUD operations, and AI-powered scheduling features.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n1. Set up your environment variables in the collection\n2. Run the \"Login\" request to get an access token\n3. The token will be automatically stored and used for subsequent requests\n4. Explore the API endpoints and test the features\n\n## Features\n\n- ðŸ” JWT Authentication\n- ðŸ‘¥ Employee Management\n- ðŸ“‹ Schedule Rules (with NLP parsing)\n- ðŸ“… Schedule Management\n- ðŸ”” Notifications\n- ðŸ¤– AI Schedule Generation\n- ðŸ“Š Analytics\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n- `base_url`: API base URL (default: http://localhost:8000)\n- `access_token`: JWT access token (auto-populated)\n- `manager_email`: Manager email for login\n- `manager_password`: Manager password\n- `employee_email`: Employee email for testing\n- `employee_password`: Employee password",
